languages.text: "К ору... погодите-ка! Это же {mf|Его|Ее} Светлость фон Валанциус! Ох, я уж решил, псы Чорды снова с проверкой пожаловали... отбой тревоги!"
"To arms— wait! It's {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship} von Valancius! I thought it was Chorda's dogs with another inspection... Stand down. False alarm."

languages.text: « Aux arm... Attendez ! C'est Sa Seigneurie von Valancius ! J'ai cru que les chiens de Chorda revenaient faire une inspection... Fausse alerte. Baissez vos armes. »
languages.original_text: "To arms— wait! It's {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship} von Valancius! I thought it was Chorda's dogs with another inspection... Stand down. False alarm."

languages.text: "An die Waffen ... wartet! Das ist {mf|Seine Lordschaft|Ihre Ladyschaft} von Valancius! Ich dachte, Chordas Hunde kämen zu einer neuerlichen Inspektion ... Entspannt euch. Falscher Alarm."
languages.original_text: "To arms— wait! It's {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship} von Valancius! I thought it was Chorda's dogs with another inspection... Stand down. False alarm."

languages.text: “举起武器——等等！原来是冯·瓦兰修斯大人！我还以为是库尔达的走狗又来搜查了……放下武器，都没事儿了。”
languages.original_text: "To arms— wait! It's {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship} von Valancius! I thought it was Chorda's dogs with another inspection... Stand down. False alarm."

languages.text: «¡A las armas!... ¡Un momento! ¡Es su excelencia von Valancius! Pensaba que los perros de Chorda volvían para otra inspección... Calma todo el mundo, falsa alarma».
